args: Yue, may I have a moment?
It's about the fiends we took down\nrecently. I was wonder... Huh?
Why do you look like you're\npacking for a journey?
Because it's time for me to go!
Yep. See, if you hunt for too long in the\nsame location, all the game there will\neventually disappear.
So my people always move on to a\nnew site before that happens.
This all seems very sudden.\nDoes Cleo know your plans?
Actually, I was sorta hoping to slip out in\nthe night without a whole lot of fuss.
I don't think I could go if I had to look\nCleo in the eyes and say good-bye.
Are you sure you have to go, Yue?\nWe'll all miss you terribly.
Look, it's not like I won't be sad either!\nBut it's just that... I mean...
We got fiends in the nearby village!
Got it. We'll head out right away.
Of course! We'll get rowdy one last time as\nthanks for everything you've done for me.
Looks like that was the last one.
Look at this place. It's a disaster!\nThe trees and the grass are shredded,\nand the animals are all hurt!
When fiends attack, they destroy\neverything around them.
I am pleased you made it back safely.
Thanks, Cleo—and thanks for keeping\nan eye on things here in the castle.
Welcome back to you as well, Yue.
What is it, Yue? You're awfully quiet.
*sigh* You probably got so rough and\nrowdy that you're hungry, yes?
If fiends continue rampaging here,\nthe woods are going to die.
Then the animals will vanish, and then...
Well, then everyone will be hungry!
I can't let that happen! Right now,\nthe most important thing is to stop\nthe fiends. ...Right?
That's right. Fiends aren't a part of\nnature. Leaving them unchecked\ncould be disastrous.
Right? So, then... I mean, I really\nshouldn't but...and maybe you'll\nthink I'm just sad to leave, but...
I mean, I AM sad!\nBut I also need to leave...but...
Fine! I'll stay here and fight fiends\nwith all of you!
Is that okay, {player_name}?\nOr is it a mistake?
No, Yue. It's not a mistake.

You told me about how important it was
not to stay too long in one place, but if
there's something unnatural there harming
everything, you have to destroy it.
So will you stay and fight with us?
I'm sorry, but what's going on here?
Oh, um...nothing.  It's all been sorted.
Well, I suppose I'm glad if it's already\nbeen resolved, but...
There's something I want to say, Cleo.
Er, all right? What is it?
I'm SUPER hungry from fighting,\nand I WANT FOOOOOOD!
*sigh* So this WAS about your bottomless\nstomach after all.
Ha ha! That's very you, Yue.
Yep! A little chow after getting rough with\nthe fiends is just what the hunter ordered!
Wonder what's on the menu today? Nya ha!
